      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in a vehicle that\u2019s full of personality and ready for more adventures! This car is in fair condition, showing some honest signs of its journey so far, but it remains a dependable and practical choice. It\u2019s perfect for someone looking for a reliable ride at a great price!",
