    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my car, and I think you\u2019re going to love it. It\u2019s in really nice shape and has been super reliable for all my trips around town. It\u2019s a smooth ride, looks great, and is ready to go whenever you are! I\u2019ve taken good care of it, so it\u2019s clean and ready for its next owner to enjoy. Perfect for daily commutes or weekend fun. Let me know if you want to come check it out!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
